{"id": "1255712412443607091", "channel_id": "1255712412443607091", "type": 0, "author_id": "1112189464140324947", "author_name": "timee_ky", "author_bot": false, "content": "大家好，这里是提米。米粒的加入为深海多队带来了很多可能性，以往的容灾我一般使用三队深海(国家队，水母，鲨鱼)进行处理，这次容灾使用了四队，整体深海灵活性得到进一步提高。\n很快乐能看到纯色队的发展，深海主打练度碾压所以随着时间推移对于350的奖励会拿的越来越容易一些，然后纯色队因为都在一个池子里也相对比较好抽适合养成。十分期待后续的深海角色。", "timestamp": "2024-06-27T02:32:49.135000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [{"emoji": "🍟", "emoji_id": null, "count": 7}, {"emoji": "2neko_excited", "emoji_id": "1200338617403461715", "count": 1}], "attachments": [{"id": "1255712412661842030", "filename": "Screenshot_2024-06-27-02-49-39-701_com.qookkagames.z1.gw.hk.jpg", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 175491, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1255712412443607091/1255712412661842030/Screenshot_2024-06-27-02-49-39-701_com.qookkagames.z1.gw.hk.jpg?ex=69fb5111&is=69f9ff91&hm=6d7173fb334fe20e0104dcd2a11711fd2b3f7a0885818b8c3a15b9517394fd8c&"}], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1255712412443607091", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "容灾350四深海队", "forum_channel_id": "1174179624096378930", "is_thread_starter": true, "thread_tags": ["1260133992636743681", "1174179716706619494"]}
{"id": "1255886422926295152", "channel_id": "1255886422926295152", "type": 0, "author_id": "1020614423880159232", "author_name": "c0d1st", "author_bot": false, "content": "凹了一两天终于过融灾350咯~特此发帖庆祝，记录一下。\n第一波：希洛萝坦，头铁顶过去，不知道咋过的\n第二波：打的-4，没想到借了泥工的24组传统混沌24，这关反而是凹得最久的（），攻防数值只够硬顶到第8回合，试了好几次才杀。。\n第三波：深海炖鸡+触手队，纯盾击打的没回得多，遂把墨菲换米粒，苦痛圣腕太强了，但最后大头还是盾击的伤害，米粒成长实在太慢了<:flop:1236937860922343466> \n第四波：用自己的混沌24第一关就得爆死抗，结果换了鲨凯队出人意料地轻松，一路都是一群群的小怪靠鲨鱼大招割草，最后鲨鱼打希洛懂得都懂，感觉如果把镜像刻给强者为尊死扛都不用掉\n第五波：打的-2，尤乌队挺简单打，本来还想卡臭脚回合把他爆了结果原来boss只有一条血，-3出门就寄，打不过根本打不过<:Coffee:1240919421791375380> \n总结：首先肥肠感谢书生佬和各位群的答疑解惑，其次5-3真不知道咋打，尤乌启动太慢了谁来都一样~\n\n下面贴下之前打的链接\nhttps://discord.com/channels/1131791637933199470/1250736319496454145", "timestamp": "2024-06-27T14:04:16.467000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [{"emoji": "🍟", "emoji_id": null, "count": 9}], "attachments": [{"id": "1255886423568154665", "filename": "Screenshot_2024-06-27-21-44-46-055_com.qookkagames.z1.gp.hk.jpg", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 139636, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1255886422926295152/1255886423568154665/Screenshot_2024-06-27-21-44-46-055_com.qookkagames.z1.gp.hk.jpg?ex=69fb4a60&is=69f9f8e0&hm=185df5efff28504c8055325531afe9309e7d5e2bde1fb53e9b29862ba2a7e7c4&"}, {"id": "1255886424008294410", "filename": "Screenshot_2024-06-27-21-44-51-913_com.qookkagames.z1.gp.hk.jpg", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 140075, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1255886422926295152/1255886424008294410/Screenshot_2024-06-27-21-44-51-913_com.qookkagames.z1.gp.hk.jpg?ex=69fb4a60&is=69f9f8e0&hm=aa38cd9d7c5e7fbb9831e5123b9f4fda8d5b554c937b6e1ef3176c80ac03f8e7&"}, {"id": "1255886424318939297", "filename": "Screenshot_2024-06-27-21-45-01-928_com.qookkagames.z1.gp.hk.jpg", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 139267, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1255886422926295152/1255886424318939297/Screenshot_2024-06-27-21-45-01-928_com.qookkagames.z1.gp.hk.jpg?ex=69fb4a60&i